        Put the dist on github

0.02    2008-10-25  Rhesa Rozendaal <rhesa@cpan.org>
        Bumped prereq of Devel::Declare

0.01    2008-10-23  Rhesa Rozendaal <rhesa@cpan.org>
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

